content: About 2 weeks into use and So far it's amazing app

Loved this enough in the free version to purchase it. It's easy to record your recurring and one time bills! The green/red dots on the calendar are fantastic to visual see what's paid and not. The only reason I gave it 4 stars is that the file names are different for the backup files between the free version and paid. You have to be a bit tech savvy to figure it out; I almost requested a refund!
paid for this app but it still does not back-up via SD card or google account. please do something about this. also, please add option to view list or calendar.

I like the free version, so I paid for it. But none of the data transfers to the paid version. I had to manually rename the folders/ files so that I could import the data. Both versions should use the same file naming format to avoid this in the future.
Keep up the good work please add custom alert options
